(58, 'Graphics Manual', 'The Graphics Manual is an organizing of my "technology" bookmark research as it relates to Graphics.\r\nI. 3D Animation & Gaming\r\n	A. Languages:\r\n		1. Javascript\r\n		2. Python\r\n			a. Scripts\r\n\r\n	B. Software\r\n		1. Cinema 4D\r\n		2. Blender  http://www.blender.org/\r\n		3. Blend4Web\r\n	C. Game Engines\r\n		1. ThreeJS \r\n			SOURCE: https://github.com/mrdoob/three.js/  \r\n			GATEWAY: http://threejs.org/\r\n			a. Interactive Examples\r\n				i. Space Debris (inkfood)\r\n				ii. Stemkoski\r\n			b. quick modeling tools( besides blender)\r\n				i. http://callum.com  interactive template\r\n\r\n\r\n		2. ThreeX { game extensions }\r\n		3. Other game engines\r\n			a. babylonjs\r\n\r\n	D. TESTING ENVIRONMENT\r\n		1. CocoonJS\r\n\r\n	E. VoodooJS ( Mixing 3d and 2D content)\r\n\r\n	F. General Resources\r\n		1. BVH files\r\n		2. BV Hacker http://www.3dartistonline.com/news/2011/03/free-blender-tutorial/\r\n\r\n\r\nII. 2D Animation & Interactivity\r\n	A. Languages\r\n		1. Javscript\r\n		2. Actionscript\r\n			a. Scripts\r\n				i. http://snipplr.com/\r\n\r\n	B. Software\r\n		1. Adobe Edge\r\n		2. Flash\r\n		3. FlashDevelop\r\n		4. Swish\r\n		5. Adobe Flex\r\n	C. Libraries\r\n		1. Raphael http://raphaeljs.com/\r\n\r\n\r\nIII. Graphics\r\n	A. Photoshop\r\n	B. Illustrator\r\n	C. Gimp\r\n	D. Inkscape\r\n	E. Job Types\r\n		1. Create a spherical map\r\n			a. lizardlounge.com\r\n', '', 1),
