did they come from to get to our site, to ask for a demo.\r\n                4) Anyone who tries to contact us via the form\r\n                5) anyone who clicks on the phone number or email links\r\n                6) which videos did they watch(5)\r\n                7) our social media buttons\r\n                                A. You Tube\r\n                                B. Twitter\r\n                                C. Facebook\r\n                                D. G+\r\n                8) what search terms did they enter in our search mechanism\r\n\r\n*/', '', 1),
