(256, 'WAI compliance', 'Backup zip for jppa work.\r\n\r\nResource links:\r\nhttps://www.w3.org/WAI/\r\nRequired:\r\n1)	Alt text\r\nâ€¢	This is for links (In the case of titles on the links), and for images(alt text on the images). This is priority, and must be handled first.\r\n2)	Keyboard input rather than having to always use a mouse\r\nâ€¢	Anywhere on the website that there is a button, we need to provide an option for the user to use a keyboard command to continue. This is for elderly people and people with disabilities regarding motor skills. It is recognized by the â€œUN Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilitiesâ€.\r\n3)	Text transcript for videos\r\nâ€¢	Instructions on how to do these transcripts can be found at https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/2734799?hl=en\r\n', 'WAI-Compliance.zip', 3),
