(268, 'business newspaper software', ' \r\n NEWSPAPER SOFTWARE EXAMPLE FEATURES:\r\n bulletlink.com\r\n\r\nFeatures\r\nFREE MOBILE APPS\r\nMarket is moving fast towards viewing news content over mobile devices. Developing such apps that has complex requirements and cost thousands of dollars. In addition to low monthly cost, bulletlink.com offers FREE apps for both iOS (Apple) and Android (Google). There is no setup fees for website or both apps.\r\nFREE CUSTOMIZATION\r\nbulletlink.com continues to offer templates that meets latest design trends and technology . You can choose template during signup and still change to another template anytime in future. You can also mix and match portions from template to another or just bring in your own design and we will do it for you.\r\nFREE 24X7 SUPPORT\r\nWe have exceptional free 24x7x365 support system where our support staff standing by to help you with questions or issues within minutes.\r\n10-DAY MONEY BACK\r\nNot satisfied with our service? No worries, get a full refund within 10 days. There is no contract whatsoever.\r\nPASSWORD-PROTECTED\r\nAllow optional password protection on selected sections to restrict site access.\r\nUNLIMITED ARTICLES\r\nUpload as many articles, stories or photos as you like.\r\nSITE SEARCH\r\nAdd value to your website by allowing visitors to search for information on your website. A search box with issue date and keywords is automatically placed onto your website or use Google Custom Search that is also automatically available on your sites.\r\nACCEPT CREDIT CARDS\r\nSetup merchant account with your bank and start accepting payments with credit cards with no extra cost. We support over 50 gateways for processing credit cards online or use PayPal free online payment service.\r\nSUBSCRIBERS TO EMAIL\r\nAllow readers to sign up to receive headline news from your website.Our system automatically creates HTML newsletter that you can email to your subscribers using third-party services.\r\nPHOTO GALLERY\r\nWe constantly add different styles of photo galleries for you to from. Visit our template show case and see some examples or bring in your own design and we will customize for you.\r\nMULTIPLE USERS\r\nCreate multiple Site Manager logins and assign selected functionalities to these users.\r\nSHOPPING CART\r\nBuild, manage and sell products online. Donâ€™t worry if youâ€™re new to e-commerce; our system is designed to help you every step of the way.\r\nRESPONSIVE WEBSITES\r\nAs per latest web trends and technology, bulletlink.com creates websites to provide an optimal viewing experience - easy reading and navigation with a minimum of resizing, panning, and scrolling - across a wide range of devices.\r\nGOOGLE AD-SENSE\r\nOur software system supports Google Ad-Sense advertising as well as any third-party advertising systems. All you have to do is copy and paste scripts fro third-party vendors in to our systems.\r\nRSS / XML FEEDS\r\nReally Simple Syndication) is an XML-based format for sharing and distributing Web content, such as news headlines. With RSS reader software, your readers can view latest news headlines along with short news description from your website.\r\nUNLIMITED FORMS\r\nCreate forms and interact with your visitors. Feed-back forms are used to let website visitors contact you directly from your website. With few clicks, you can easily setup HTML forms and requires NO HTML programming skills at all.\r\nCOMMENTS\r\nAllow readers to comment or post their opinion directly on an article. Other website visitors can also view other opinion or comments entries on your site.\r\nPROPERTY LISTINGS\r\nAllows you to display property listings including agents'' bio-data. This is another way to generate more revenue for your business.\r\nPOLLS\r\nCreate interactive surveys, polls, for your web site. It helps you learn more about your customers.\r\nSITEMAP\r\nOur software automatically creates sitemaps for all major search engines crawlers.\r\nWIDGETS/GADGETS