(340, 'inmotion reseller contact', 'InMotion Hosting\r\nchat SALES CHAT\r\nphone 888.321.HOST(4678)\r\nINTERNATIONAL: +1-757-416-6575\r\n SKYPE\r\n SECURE SERVERMcAfee Secure\r\nWelcome to InMotion Hosting, Inc.!\r\nYour order is in the account setup process now and you will receive an initial email confirmation in the next few minutes. A New Account Specialist will contact you by phone to confirm your order and ensure you have everything you need to get started.\r\n\r\nGenerally, we make these calls within 30 minutes of your order, but it may take longer if you ordered between 10PM and 8AM Eastern Standard Time.\r\n\r\nWhile you''re waiting...\r\n\r\nFeel free to learn more about customizing your hosting account with your Account Management Panel (AMP) and Control Panel (cPanel) in our article, AMP vs. cPanel.\r\n\r\nSpecial Offer: InMotion Hosting''s line of premium business websites offer the perfect solution to get your business online, no matter what your budget. Reach new customers by letting our expert web designers create a search engine optimized website for your business! For a limited time, get a FREE 5 minute website consultation! Call (888) 710-7483 for details!\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to contact us if you have any questions.\r\nsupport@inmotionhosting.com\r\nPH: 757-416-6575\r\nPH: 888-321-HOST (4678)\r\nOr visit our Customer Center', '', 3),
