(699, 'dispenser', 'Dispenser\r\n\r\nHOW TO :\r\nWorking With Plexy Glass:------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nglue-ing plexy glass( syringe and acryllic glue and masking tap and square)\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P7OkCOlF7Ds\r\n\r\ncut plexy glass: ( oscillating tool ) \r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XPlbZdwQ2AM\r\n\r\ndrill through plexy glass ( drill press and metal drill bits )\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hM_DR3t4mjI\r\n\r\nengrave design on plexy glass: ( dremel engraver tool )\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XPph6mi7U0E\r\n\r\nMaterials: --------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nPlexiglass \r\n12 in. x 24 in. x .093 in. Clear Polycarbonate Sheet  $17.00\r\nhttps://www.homedepot.com/p/LEXAN-12-in-x-24-in-x-093-in-Clear-Polycarbonate-Sheet-GE-33/202038063\r\n\r\nLOCTITE GO2 glue\r\n$5 @ home depot\r\n\r\nPlaskolite- Pro Cutter for Plexiglass\r\n$5\r\n\r\nsuction cups:\r\nwith brass nut ($6 each )\r\nhttps://www.ebay.com/itm/20-BEST-1-7-8-SUCTION-CUP-WITH-8-32-Stud-Nut-Heavy-Duty-Commercial-Rated-/263497276330\r\n\r\n50pc set ( $5 )\r\nhttps://www.ebay.com/p/50pcs-Clear-Transparent-Hanger-Kitchen-Bathroom-Suction-Cup-Sucker-20mm/1293908432?iid=253610782887&_trkparms=aid%3D555018%26algo%3DPL.SIM%26ao%3D2%26asc%3D50544%26meid%3D042a9cb7decf44ff9614a694516091df%26pid%3D100005%26rk%3D4%26rkt%3D12%26mehot%3Dlo%26sd%3D263497276330%26itm%3D253610782887&_trksid=p2047675.c100005.m1851\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTOOLS:-------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nBosch Oscillating tool $50 \r\nhttps://louisville.craigslist.org/tls/d/bosch-oscillating-tool-kit/6599488448.html\r\n\r\nDremel Oscillating tool: $50\r\nhttps://www.ebay.com/itm/Dremel-2-5-Amp-Multi-Max-Oscillating-Tool-Kit-MM30-01-Reconditioned/331804286558?epid=1985211868&hash=item4d41139e5e:g:Q6EAAOSwL3JauamU:sc:ShippingMethodStandard!47122!US!-1\r\n\r\ncircular saw blade 140 teeth $10\r\nhttps://ww