n   I.  E-Commerce Site for orders and payments\r\n\r\n\r\nShopping Strategy:\r\nbring measuring tape\r\n\r\n$18 for small plexy glass sheet\r\n$4 for ball valve pvc\r\n$5 glue\r\n$5 cutter\r\n$10 drill bit \r\n\r\n$42 \r\nactually:\r\n$5.98 acryllic sheet ( .093x11x14)\r\n$2.97 masking tape\r\n$5.96 command picture hanging velcro\r\n$4.98 pro cut tool\r\n$13.97 shockwave hole saw\r\n$.55 1/2" pvc coupling\r\n$.39 1/2" pvc elbow 90deg\r\n$.85 1/2" pvc elbow 45deg\r\n\r\nPREMADE BOXES about $2.00 each \r\nhttps://www.shoppopdisplays.com/CS001/5-sided-clear-acrylic-box-custom-size.html\r\n\r\n\r\nCommand Velcro strips 6 pairs about  1 dollar a pair.\r\n2 pairs on each box = $2.00\r\n\r\n\r\nClear Tubing at Home Depot\r\n$9 for 5 feet of 1/2 " clear tubing.\r\n$13.50 5 feet of 1" clear acryllic tubing\r\n\r\nhttps://www.homedepot.com/p/Formufit-1-2-in-x-5-ft-Furniture-Grade-Sch-40-PVC-Pipe-in-Clear-P012FGP-UV/206028369?cm_mmc=Shopping%7CG%7CBase%7CD26P%7C26-1_PIPE_AND_FITTINGS%7CNA%7CPLA%7c71700000033850297%7c58700003917961062%7c92700031584468599&gclid=CjwKCAjwrqnYBRB-EiwAthnBFpCvOEbwqd6ZA5FinKCwlbuSAojq_y57_2crQFRUxejoPt2yGo8xsxoC0ZsQAvD_BwE&dclid=CPy71KbfptsCFUtqAQodtI8AdA\r\n\r\n\r\n2 clear caps: drill 1/2" holes for tube\r\n$5 !!!\r\n\r\nblack pvc 1 inch caps:\r\n$1.03\r\nhttps://www.pvcfittingsonline.com/1-pvc-end-cap-furniture-grade-black.html?matchtype=&network=g&device=c&adposition=1o2&keyword=&gclid=CjwKCAjwrqnYBRB-EiwAthnBFhu8MTkIh8cv4b2riTGXstoOk-7CpMeJ_9MhJ27LGOimSlLWx3DEBRoCqxcQAvD_BwE\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '', 3),
